# Sinatra RESTful Routes

| CRUD Letter | RESTful Route           | Controller Action |
|-------------|-------------------------|-------------------|
| C(reate)    |                         | create            |
| R(ead)      | GET /dishes             | index             |
| R(ead)      | GET  /dishes/:id        | show              |
| U(pdate)    |                         | update            |
| D(elete)    |                         | destroy           |


